name: cluster3b_3 avg
query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(t.title) AS movie_title FROM cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, name AS n, title AS t WHERE ci.note IN ('(producer)', '(executive producer)') AND it1.info = 'budget' AND it2.info = 'votes' AND n.gender = 'm' AND n.name LIKE '%Tim%' AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id;
